Class ConfigFileResolvingHttpRequestFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.http.client.AbstractClientHttpRequestFactoryWrapper
      • org.mapfish.print.ConfigFileResolvingHttpRequestFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.http.client.ClientHttpRequestFactory

    public final class ConfigFileResolvingHttpRequestFactory
extends org.springframework.http.client.AbstractClientHttpRequestFactoryWrapper
    This request factory will attempt to load resources using Configuration.loadFile(String) and Configuration.isAccessible(String) to load the resources if the http method is GET and will fallback to the normal/wrapped factory to make http requests.
